= Arno Pro Optical Text

Arno Pro body text uses the Regular optical-size face at 11 points.

#text(size: 8pt)[Caption text uses Arno Pro Caption.]

#text(size: 10pt)[Small text uses Arno Pro SmText.]

#text(size: 18pt)[Subhead text uses Arno Pro Subhead.]

#text(size: 24pt)[Display text uses Arno Pro Display.]

#text(
  weight: "semibold",
  size: 10pt,
)[Semibold small text uses Arno Pro Smbd SmText.]
